metadata.name: SOBI: Edition one - Genesis Key
metadata.description:
The Society of Black Innovators is a community of action and support. Our goal is to create a space where black artists, musicians, entrepreneurs, and devs, can come together and create. Collaboration is the key to creating a better world

Here are some of the things we have planned for our community:  
 - Pitch competitions (receive funding for your idea)  
- Special guest 
- Weekly art buys ( We buy nfts from our community members every week)  
- Think Tank ( The community will ideate and vote on an innovative project to execute)
